{"word":"G615 - ἀποκτείνω - apokteínō - ap-ok-ti'-no - Put to death","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκτείνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apokteínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok-ti'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Put to death</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொல், அழி, கொலைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to kill in any way"},{"paragraph":"2. to extinguish, abolish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>kteino&#x0304;</b> (to <i>slay</i>); to <i>kill</i> outright; figuratively to <i>destroy:</i> - put to death, kill, slay.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}